subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Eskimos
Native Americans
lead_paragraph: John Baker crossed the finish line first in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race to reclaim the title of Iditarod champion for an Alaska Native musher.
